replies.bodyText:
Because Spark 3 relocate this class: WriterCommitMessage.
In Spark 2, it's:
import org.apache.spark.sql.sources.v2.writer.WriterCommitMessage;

In Spark 3, it's:
import org.apache.spark.sql.connector.write.WriterCommitMessage;

That's why we cannot use a single class to do this.

